summary: Female Led 'Fast & Furious' Spinoff in the Works
title: Female Led 'Fast & Furious' Spinoff in the Works
body:
A new #Fast&Furious spinoff is reportedly in development, which will bring the females to the forefront.

The Fast & Furious is one of the most beloved franchises in movies in the last 20 years. Ya, you read that right 20 years. The first film in the franchise was released in 2001 and has since produced 8 total films spanning 2001-2019. Of course all the movies haven’t been box office hits, and of course the untimely death of the Paul Walker also have given the franchise its share of down moments.…

summary: Look who was on clearance! I'm especially excited to have found Venom, he has become difficult to find at all. Its a bit sad to...
body:
Look who was on clearance! I’m especially excited to have found Venom, he has become difficult to find at all.

Its a bit sad to see the tsum tsum section going away, but “A thing isn’t beautiful because it lasts”. ;)

I’m not even sure if marvel tsums are completely dead. There was that large WS plush that showed up, which was definitely a knockoff, but now there is apparently going to be a large Loki plush? Exclusive to Shanghai Disney? Hope that means there’s more coming. (Either way, I need that Loki!)
